Author: fishonthesun
Text: <3 thank you for your reply, it means a lot to me. If it's the only thing I eat that day I might be able to not feel bad about it. It's not till tomorrow so I guess I have time to panic and get over it and try to enjoy time with my friends

Author: n0kikin0ki
Text: leading up to my wedding, i had big meals with family almost every night for a week. at the end of it all, i expected to have a massive gain but in fact, i didn't gain anything at all. your body needs more calories than you think. i know it's hard but just remember this life is for living and one day of having fun with your friends and eating delicious food isn't going to magically make you fat.
